---
title: BBQ Buffalo Tofu Sammies with Creamy Slaw and Potato Coins
description: The perfect pub-night dinner has been transformed to a sandwich! Creamy slaw and tender tofu tossed in a honey-butter sauce is served on a toasted bun alongside potato coins. Enjoy!

